This program accepts the following TOOLTYPE options.

@{fg HIGHLIGHT}@{u}Tooltype                Value           Description                         @{uu}@{fg text}

@{fg FILL}WARNINGS                @{fg SHINE}TRUE  | ON      @{fg TEXT}Novice requester warnings on.
                        @{fg SHINE}FALSE | OFF     @{fg TEXT}Novice requester warnings on.

@{fg FILL}BUFFER                  @{fg SHINE}HALFRAW         @{fg TEXT}Initial compaction buffer setting.
                        @{fg SHINE}QUARTERRAW
                        @{fg SHINE}ONEHALFIFF

@{fg FILL}DISPLAY                 @{fg SHINE}ANIM            @{fg TEXT}What to display while converting.
                        @{fg SHINE}PROGRESS

@{fg FILL}SAVEICONS               @{fg SHINE}TRUE  | ON      @{fg TEXT}Save icon with the SFMV anim.
                        @{fg SHINE}FALSE | OFF     @{fg TEXT}Don't save the icon.
@ENDNODE
